channel.title: Cache trouble
channel.description: hey guys so i posted a topic not to long ago about my items being nulls, anyway i deleted my cache and added another 377 cache (yes i know there pretty much all the same), i also went to my client.java and found 0xfffff so i knew the original source was a 377 so there was no need to change anything, but now when i run the client it it makes it about halfway through then it comes up with that ("couldnt load this server, 1.restart your browser, 2.....") screen and i have no choice but to exit and sit on the problem for half an hour rofl, what exactly did i do wrong?( yes i changed it back to my other cache and it works fine and half of my items are still nulls,) How do i fix this "null" situation and how exactly do i get my 377 cache to work? can someone please help me :) thanks! (this is a 317 blank source and client) The one im using:http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=407757.0
